make sure you have all the HW that are in the "HW used" file.
make the correct connections just like the connection diagram.
open the esp code using arduino app.
make sure you use your parameters in the currect places descriped in the Parameters folder.
upload the code to esp32 using a micro usb cable.
after that you should use the included app and the firebase for communications.
you should be all set for using our project.
